      "title": "Kandakkadu Rushing Human Rights Commission",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An investigation team of the Sri Lanka Human Rights Commission will go there today (01) to investigate the conflict that took place at the Kantakadu Rehabilitation Centre.",
        "Investigations are going to be conducted regarding the death of a person who was detained there and the collision incident.",
        "Following the clash at the Kandakadu Rehabilitation Center, most of the detainees had escaped."
